Hi,
@aselle can you educate me more about inception5h. I would like to know why there is a time difference between inceptionV3 and inception5h models(Like why is it not inceptionV5, why is it not listed in the models list here, is inceptionV5 retrained on some other models like inceptionV3?).

As @left13 mentioned, even I am able to run the demo(5h model) at 170ms-450ms on each prediction on OnePlus3T device and my retrained &optimized v3 at 1500ms-2100ms

@left13 I tried eight-bit calculations. The inference time has slightly improved to 1200ms~1500ms, but the classification part dosent work, for any image you pass, it shows a constant output(Tested on OnePlus3T device).

I understand from my experiments that after quantization or eight-bit calculations, the size of APK/model has decreased from 82.1 MB to 19.6MB but the result is same:"Image classification dosent work"

Is it possible to retrain inception5h model on my own data?
